                <h4>Installation</h4>
                <p>Install composer and run the following command from your project folder</p>
                <pre><code class="bash">
composer require andrevanzuydam\tina4php
                </code></pre>
                    <h4>index.php</h4><p>Create an index.php file in your project folder after composer has installed the library, add the following code</p>
                <pre><code class="php">&lt;?php
require "vendor/autoload.php";
echo new \Tina4\Tina4Php();</code></pre>

                <h4>Run your application</h4>
                <pre><code class="bash">
php -S localhost:7124 index.php
                </code></pre>
